    <item>
      <title>英国央行前副行长将领导对英国水务行业的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/former-boe-deputy-governor-to-lead-review-into-uk-water-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行前副行长乔恩·康利夫将领导对英国私有水务行业的重大审查，因为该行业正面临公众因污水泄漏和水费上涨而日益高涨的愤怒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/former-boe-deputy-governor-to-lead-review-into-uk-water-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦财政部长认为中国债务谈判“令人鼓舞”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/pakistan-says-debt-reprofile-talks-with-china-are-encouraging</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦财政部长表示，巴基斯坦关于延长“一带一路”贷款期限的请求得到了中国的积极回应，这意味着过去因高昂借贷成本而陷入困境的国家可能将获得更多喘息空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/pakistan-says-debt-reprofile-talks-with-china-are-encouraging</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 19:08:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
